<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/3072> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #3072" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "A son of the Consul of 178, who attained the praetorship and was noted for his knowledge of the civil law (Pompon. Dig. 1.2.2.39; cf. Cic. Brut. 130)." .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/2988> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #2988" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Named in the Bembinus Ms of the Didascalia of Terence Eun. (see note 1). Dziatzko's dating in 146 (RhM 21 [1866] 66) is doubted by Seidel (FA 79) since it is unlikely that in this period a plebeian and a patrician would be colleagues in this office." .
